Gluten Free Cookie Cheesecake Minis
Cookie crust mini cheesecakes with cinnamon
classic
Sweet, Soft, Spiced

INGREDIENTS:
Cookie Crust: 3/8 cup butter, 1/2 cup white sugar, 1/4 cup brown sugar
1 egg, 1 1/4 cups gluten-free flour, 1/2 tsp vanilla
1/4 tsp salt, 1/2 tsp cinnamon
Filling: 16oz cream cheese (room temp)
1/2 cup sour cream (room temp)
1/2 cup white sugar
2 eggs
1 tsp vanilla

INSTRUCTIONS:
Cream butter and sugars. Add egg and vanilla, mix. Add flour, salt, cinnamon. Refrigerate
Preheat oven to 350Â°F
Make filling: Cream cheese and sugar. Add sour cream, eggs, vanilla. Refrigerate
Press dough into greased muffin tin bottoms. Pre-bake 5-7 minutes
Add filling (less than 1/4 cup per cavity). Bake 18-20 minutes until edges brown
Cool 20-30 minutes, remove from tin
Refrigerate at least 1 hour before serving. Makes 24 minis